C h a n g e L o g
=================

Here is the list of all { significant | noteworthy | major | et al }
changes to the implementation.

The file NEWS contains a chronology of releases and major versions.

 -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=--=-=-=-=-=-

2008-07-27  Rocco Carbone <rocco /at/ tecsiel /dot/ it>
	* Initial public release 0.1.0 announced to libvent mailing list

	  FEATURES:
	  * Runs under Linux 2.6.18
	  * Uses libevent-1.4.5-stable
	  * Has a demonstration main application 'noah'
	  * Distribution includes both tutorial and production plugins
	  * General documentation have been written
	  * Minimal html download area at http://ark.tecsiel.it [82.187.228.118]
